  "description": "Product Description:\n\nExude elegance with this exquisite lab-grown emerald ring, crafted in high-quality S925 sterling silver with a classic four-prong setting. The sterling silver band is durable and hypoallergenic, ensuring a comfortable and long-lasting wear.\n\nThe centerpiece of this ring is a striking 9x14mm, 4.26-carat emerald-cut lab-grown emerald that captures attention with its deep green hue and flawless clarity. Flanking each side of the central stone are three rows of colorless emerald-cut accent stones, totaling 0.48 carats, arranged in precise alignment to enhance the brilliance of the main stone. This statement piece weighs 6.58 grams and is available in U.S. sizes 5 to 7.5. Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings ship within 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Emerald Center Stone: A 9x14mm, 4.26-carat emerald-cut gem, symbolizing refined elegance and sophistication.\n\nElegant Side Accents: Three rows of colorless emerald-cut stones on each side, adding extra sparkle and depth.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Crafted in hypoallergenic and tarnish-resistant sterling silver for durability and style.\n\nPerfect Fit: Available in U.S. ring sizes 5 to 7.5.\n\nShipping: Lab-grown colored gemstone rings have an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days.\n\nA blend of timeless sophistication and modern luxury, this ring is the perfect statement piece for anyone seeking elegance and exclusivity in their jewelry collection.",
